1
00:01:28,920 --> 00:01:30,200
You knew from the time you arrived in Harbor City

2
00:01:30,959 --> 00:01:32,760
that they were looking for the jade on me.

3
00:01:34,959 --> 00:01:35,760
No.

4
00:01:36,480 --> 00:01:37,680
You came for it too.

5
00:01:38,439 --> 00:01:39,239
No.

6
00:01:40,239 --> 00:01:41,439
I only found out later.

7
00:01:42,159 --> 00:01:42,959
Trust me.

8
00:01:43,959 --> 00:01:44,799
Personally and professionally,

9
00:01:45,959 --> 00:01:47,599
you are the person I must protect.

10
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:51,599
Now the Central Hotel

11
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:53,000
is full of spies.

12
00:01:53,359 --> 00:01:54,359
It's very dangerous.

13
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:56,319
It's too risky

14
00:01:56,680 --> 00:01:57,760
to get you involved.

15
00:01:58,200 --> 00:02:00,000
Leave now.

16
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:09,439
Take this.

17
00:02:09,879 --> 00:02:10,759
Your passport.

18
00:02:10,759 --> 00:02:11,719
Everything is in there.

19
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:13,639
Take it and go now.

20
00:02:15,159 --> 00:02:16,039
Check here.

21
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:16,879
Go.

22
00:02:22,599 --> 00:02:24,520
Go to the front driver's seat.

23
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:25,800
Follow me.

24
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:37,560
Go to the front.

25
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:44,919
Set off to the airport now.

26
00:02:44,919 --> 00:02:47,080
Buy the nearest flight to Rongzhou.

27
00:02:47,439 --> 00:02:48,639
After you arrive in Rongzhou,

28
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:49,840
someone will meet you.

29
00:02:49,919 --> 00:02:50,719
Okay?

30
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:52,639
I got it.

31
00:02:53,840 --> 00:02:54,560
What about you?

32
00:02:54,560 --> 00:02:55,439
What about you?

33
00:02:57,439 --> 00:02:58,319
Don't worry about me.

34
00:02:58,879 --> 00:02:59,879
I just want to see you

35
00:03:00,639 --> 00:03:02,120
arrive in Rongzhou safely.

36
00:03:02,680 --> 00:03:03,439
You go by car.

37
00:03:03,719 --> 00:03:04,520
I'll draw them away.

38
00:03:11,439 --> 00:03:12,879
Shen Shutu,

39
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:14,919
no matter what happens,

40
00:03:16,199 --> 00:03:17,400
you must come back alive.

41
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:41,599
Take care.

42
00:03:55,479 --> 00:03:56,719
Over there! Go!

43
00:03:57,120 --> 00:03:58,360
- Go! - Stop!

44
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:05,919
Come on!

45
00:04:08,199 --> 00:04:08,599
Don't run!

46
00:04:10,039 --> 00:04:10,840
Hurry up!

47
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:11,960
He's here! Go!

48
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:13,000
Stop!

49
00:04:21,199 --> 00:04:21,680
Where?

50
00:04:22,439 --> 00:04:23,160
You go this way,

51
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:23,920
the rest follow me.

52
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:24,879
Go!

53
00:04:45,439 --> 00:04:46,120
Mr. Shen.

54
00:04:47,639 --> 00:04:48,560
Let's go.

55
00:04:57,800 --> 00:05:00,040
I wonder how he's doing now.

56
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:18,480
Sis.

57
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:20,040
You finally answered.

58
00:05:20,639 --> 00:05:21,439
Why are you here?

59
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:22,920
Where's Shen Shutu?

60
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:24,240
He's with me.

61
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:38,040
Mr. Shen, you're quite agile.

62
00:05:38,279 --> 00:05:40,680
No wonder she's so devoted to you.

63
00:05:41,839 --> 00:05:42,879
If she knew you were always

64
00:05:42,879 --> 00:05:44,319
around her with

65
00:05:44,319 --> 00:05:45,319
ulterior motives,

66
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:48,199
would she still like you?

67
00:05:48,439 --> 00:05:50,399
You're the one with ulterior motives.

68
00:05:50,839 --> 00:05:51,639
Ke Yu'ang,

69
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:53,759
you can't get love,

70
00:05:53,759 --> 00:05:55,120
so you try to

71
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:56,920
slander your rival in love.

72
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:58,720
I tell you,

73
00:05:59,000 --> 00:05:59,959
she has

74
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:01,720
no interest in you at all.

75
00:06:04,759 --> 00:06:05,560
Rival?

76
00:06:07,759 --> 00:06:09,399
I've got a little surprise for you.

77
00:06:13,399 --> 00:06:14,879
Jiang Xun has no idea

78
00:06:14,879 --> 00:06:16,120
what you've done to her.

79
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:18,240
Don't even think about hurting her.

80
00:06:18,560 --> 00:06:19,519
I know how to protect her

81
00:06:19,519 --> 00:06:20,800
better than you do.

82
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:22,680
You should be worried

83
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:24,600
about yourself.

84
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:34,040
Let me go!

85
00:06:34,240 --> 00:06:35,439
Let me go!

86
00:06:35,439 --> 00:06:36,240
Junior.

87
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:38,399
Senior.

88
00:06:39,160 --> 00:06:40,319
Where's Shen Shutu?

89
00:06:42,519 --> 00:06:43,079
Jiang Xun!

90
00:06:43,319 --> 00:06:43,920
Jiang Xun!

91
00:06:44,879 --> 00:06:47,120
Do you really care about him that much?

92
00:06:47,519 --> 00:06:47,879
Actually, I...

93
00:06:47,879 --> 00:06:48,759
You don't have to explain.

94
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:50,399
I know what you want.

95
00:06:50,959 --> 00:06:52,399
I can give you the stuff.

96
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:53,639
Let me see him.

97
00:07:04,639 --> 00:07:05,439
Shen Shutu.

98
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:15,040
I gave you the stuff.

99
00:07:15,319 --> 00:07:16,120
Let us go.

100
00:07:17,199 --> 00:07:17,959
Take it and check it.

101
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:23,040
Senior.

102
00:07:24,199 --> 00:07:25,399
How did you become like this?

103
00:07:25,639 --> 00:07:26,240
Like what?

104
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:27,040
Xunxun.

105
00:07:27,639 --> 00:07:28,439
In your eyes,

106
00:07:29,199 --> 00:07:30,480
should I be like?

107
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:32,240
Aren't we the same kind of people?

108
00:07:32,639 --> 00:07:34,399
Don't you treat cultural relics as your faith?

109
00:07:34,560 --> 00:07:36,000
We have the same ideals.

110
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:37,439
I treat you as a good friend.

111
00:07:37,639 --> 00:07:39,480
But I don't just want to be your friend.

112
00:07:42,720 --> 00:07:43,920
You love him with all your heart.

113
00:07:44,519 --> 00:07:45,319
What about me?

114
00:07:45,720 --> 00:07:47,199
Haven't you ever thought about me?

115
00:07:47,199 --> 00:07:48,639
Why don't you think about me?

116
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:51,240
I've given you the thing.

117
00:07:51,639 --> 00:07:52,600
Please let us go.

118
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:02,560
Shen Shutu!

119
00:08:03,399 --> 00:08:04,759
What are you doing?

120
00:08:09,399 --> 00:08:10,319
Shen Shutu!

121
00:08:10,319 --> 00:08:11,000
Xunxun,

122
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:12,839
he is a sinner.

123
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:13,879
Everything he said to you

124
00:08:13,879 --> 00:08:15,199
and did for you is fake.

125
00:08:15,199 --> 00:08:16,240
He's been lying to you.

126
00:08:16,360 --> 00:08:18,600
I believe him. I trust him.

127
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:19,560
Let me go.

128
00:08:19,560 --> 00:08:20,800
I won't let you go.

129
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:21,800
How can I lose to him

130
00:08:21,800 --> 00:08:23,439
in terms of seniority?

131
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:26,040
Xunxun, don't you always want to go to Taiwan, China?

132
00:08:26,040 --> 00:08:27,079
Don't you always want to see

133
00:08:27,079 --> 00:08:27,959
the Jadeite Cabbage?

134
00:08:27,959 --> 00:08:28,759
Xunxun.

135
00:08:30,759 --> 00:08:32,200
I won't go back to Taiwan, China with you.

136
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:34,240
You'd better give up the idea.

137
00:08:43,879 --> 00:08:44,399
Shen Shutu!

138
00:08:52,799 --> 00:08:53,799
Shen Shutu!

139
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:10,639
All of you

140
00:09:50,039 --> 00:09:51,159
want the jade pendant?

141
00:09:51,279 --> 00:09:52,440
None of you will get it!

142
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:11,919
You really threw it away?

143
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:13,440
Don't worry about it.

144
00:10:13,440 --> 00:10:14,240
Just go.

145
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:16,120
Wait.

146
00:10:17,639 --> 00:10:19,159
Is the dragon pendant on you?

147
00:10:24,039 --> 00:10:24,759
Let's go.

148
00:10:36,559 --> 00:10:37,399
What time is it?

149
00:10:37,759 --> 00:10:38,720
Hurry up.

150
00:11:18,600 --> 00:11:19,679
He killed Jiang Xun.

151
00:11:51,759 --> 00:11:54,399
[We used to be like-minded fellows.]

152
00:11:54,399 --> 00:11:55,480
[But time flies,]

153
00:11:55,519 --> 00:11:56,519
[and things have changed.]

154
00:11:56,840 --> 00:11:58,639
[From the moment Ke Yu'ang chose to be a spy]

155
00:11:58,639 --> 00:12:00,279
[for foreign intelligence agencies,]

156
00:12:00,320 --> 00:12:01,919
[stealing secrets and causing destruction,]

157
00:12:02,039 --> 00:12:03,679
[we were bound to be enemies.]

158
00:12:03,919 --> 00:12:05,360
[When it comes to national security]

159
00:12:05,360 --> 00:12:06,799
[and major principles,]

160
00:12:07,159 --> 00:12:09,120
[Jiang Xun's answer is resounding.]

161
00:12:09,639 --> 00:12:10,600
[The righteousness of the nation]

162
00:12:10,600 --> 00:12:12,480
[is always the unwavering belief]

163
00:12:12,480 --> 00:12:13,799
[that every Chinese defends.]
